               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410614-name-204" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18410614-name-204" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410614-name-204" type="surname" value="DRIVER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410614-name-204" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM DRIVER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am pot-boy to Thomas Griffiths, who keeps a public house in Newgate-street. On the 4th of June, the prisoner came to the bar and called for a quartern of gin—while I was gone for it he put his arm over the window, took a bottle of rum, and ran away with it—I jumped over the bar and gave an alarm—the policeman ran after him, caught him, and brought him back with the bottle of rum—I had never seen him before—I am sure he is the person.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> What time in the morning was it? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Seven o'clock—you did not have the quartern of gin—while I was gone for it yon ran off with the bottle.</p>
